Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.51,0:00:03.83,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet. I'm not finished...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.55,0:00:06.80,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be... the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.80,0:00:09.41,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,You? The Wizard King?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.41,0:00:11.58,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,I have the ability to find out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.58,0:00:15.13,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,just how much magical power \None has with these chains.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.13,0:00:18.34,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,And you have no magic whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.75,0:00:23.35,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,You must've been born that way.\NNo wonder you couldn't get a grimoire.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.71,0:00:25.90,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,To think that you lack\Neven an ounce of magic
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.90,0:00:28.17,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,in this world where magic is everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.17,0:00:30.77,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,What a priceless find!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.41,0:00:33.53,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.53,0:00:36.24,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.17,0:00:42.99,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Then no matter how hard I try, \NI won't be able to use magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.32,0:00:46.61,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,To think that someone so pathetic existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.61,0:00:50.07,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,You won't even be able to find a job, \Nlet alone become the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.07,0:00:55.99,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure your friend, the great \Ngenius over there, mocks you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.99,0:00:58.05,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.64,0:01:01.79,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno's so amazing that he \Nwas chosen by the four-leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.64,0:01:03.68,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.68,0:01:09.90,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do a thing in this world. \NJust give up on everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.90,0:01:12.86,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,You were born a loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.49,0:01:15.60,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.09,0:01:20.91,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard I try, \Nsome things just can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.44,0:01:24.66,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going to give...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.66,0:01:25.91,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:28.08,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling a loser?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.77,0:01:32.50,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, it's true that you won't be \Nable to become the Wizard King,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.75,0:01:33.80,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.39,0:01:38.30,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,You hear that? Even your little friend \Nis telling you it's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.44,0:01:43.72,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I'm going \Nto become the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.04,0:01:46.14,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.09,0:01:48.98,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,He's no loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.15,0:01:51.19,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.28,0:01:55.28,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta's my rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.39,0:01:58.37,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.37,0:02:00.27,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,Him? Your rival?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.27,0:02:02.62,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,This brat who has no \Nmagical power whatsoever?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:07.48,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not... Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.41,0:02:13.92,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry you had to see me \Nlooking that pathetic, Yuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.92,0:02:16.55,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Just a sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.55,0:02:19.30,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna kick this guy's butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.69,0:02:36.73,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,A gri... moire?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.73,0:02:38.11,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:42.41,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that Asta \Nwouldn't have been chosen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:51.41,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta's always been that way. \NHe always does the unthinkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.32,0:02:55.37,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,He always has before... \Nand he's doing it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.81,0:03:03.18,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the Wizard King... \Nand protect you and everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.65,0:03:08.51,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna make everyone even happier! \NSo we can have even nicer things!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:11.77,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I'm gonna prove to everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.51,0:03:14.10,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Prove?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.75,0:03:18.87,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That even if you're poor... or an orphan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.20,0:03:22.99,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,you can still become the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.78,0:03:48.43,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,750)}The Boys' Promise
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.53,0:03:52.78,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Grey words can't make anything happen
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.78,0:03:55.52,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, yeah I know
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.52,0:04:00.70,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wishing to fly freely across the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:02.78,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I dreamed it all my life
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.78,0:04:06.49,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Step by step I go, though \Nit's a doubtful world 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.57,0:04:08.59,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't care how much I fall
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.59,0:04:12.06,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Instinct is my guide, I never give up
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:18.42,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To faraway future, I burst out running
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:23.82,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Go beyond even the unseen fears
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:28.97,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The vision I had, so I can be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.97,0:04:34.23,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday I will write the next page
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.23,0:04:37.75,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,You are my hope
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:40.48,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Like that page from someday
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:42.82,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to meet you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:45.78,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I call this a miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.99,0:04:59.44,sign_7118_54_10_Years_Ago,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1000)}10 Years Ago
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:00.93,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.68,0:05:09.43,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:14.97,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Yuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:17.32,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.94,0:05:23.81,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez. You're such a crybaby, Yuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.73,0:05:25.94,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.53,0:05:27.84,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:30.96,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I've got your back, Yuno! Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.19,0:05:33.99,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.30,0:05:37.00,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.57,0:05:39.51,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's waiting at the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.53,0:05:59.85,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,It's good, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.48,0:06:01.73,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.73,0:06:03.83,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's our Sister Lily.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.83,0:06:06.79,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're such an amazing cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:10.99,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,When I grow up, will you \Nmarry me and cook for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.79,0:06:16.13,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,It was Father who baked those. \NWould you like to marry him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.99,0:06:21.50,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No! You're the one I wanna marry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:24.19,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Sister! Marry me! Marry me! Marry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:26.60,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Marry me! Marry me! Marry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.21,0:06:29.55,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.09,0:06:32.35,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, it's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.35,0:06:38.06,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Sister is, um... a woman of the cloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.06,0:06:43.57,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done yet, Yuno! I won't give up \Nuntil I'm an adult, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.56,0:06:46.79,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Well, good luck with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:58.89,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,"And then the world was covered \Nin deep, deep darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.43,0:07:02.60,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Just when the demon tried \Nto destroy the world..."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:04.44,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He's not gonna get away with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:09.59,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,"...a very brave mage appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.17,0:07:16.10,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,The brave mage fought the demon \Nto bring the dawn back to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.22,0:07:21.33,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,And finally, he defeated the demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:26.86,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,The mage's light shone ever so\Nbrightly upon the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.86,0:07:29.51,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,The long, long night had come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:31.90,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,This was the dawn of our world."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.90,0:07:34.44,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.96,0:07:46.04,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,"And so, the mage was dubbed the \NWizard King and became a legend."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:48.08,flashback,Both,0000,0000,0000,,The Wizard King...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.63,0:07:52.57,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,"And they all lived happily ever after."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:09.65,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:12.90,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The Wizard King still exists, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.32,0:08:14.40,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.08,0:08:23.16,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,The title of "Wizard King" has been passed\Ndown through many generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:30.41,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,All along, they've been\Nprotecting us with their magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:35.01,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,It's because of the Wizard King that\Nthe Clover Kingdom is so peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:36.97,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:40.13,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Is the Wizard King really important?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.13,0:08:42.57,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,He's the most important after the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.39,0:08:48.87,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I've made up my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:52.36,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,About what, Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.25,0:08:56.65,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... gonna be the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:03.99,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.99,0:09:06.31,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I just wasn't expecting that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.37,0:09:09.95,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,What brought this on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.95,0:09:12.17,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he defeated the demon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.49,0:09:15.99,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That means he's super strong!\NAnd that's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:19.11,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna be cool, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.97,0:09:21.07,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:26.83,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,If I become important...\NIf I become the Wizard King,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.32,0:09:30.52,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be able to make everyone \Neven happier, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.19,0:09:37.19,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be able to wear nice clothes \Nand eat all the good food you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.19,0:09:41.12,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna make this crappy \Nlittle church huge and amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.12,0:09:42.91,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Crappy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.33,0:09:45.99,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get you whatever you want, too, Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.40,0:09:48.25,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,I'll look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:49.42,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Yuno?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:51.92,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:54.23,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,The Wizard King...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.23,0:09:56.42,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:59.56,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So, Sister! Marry me—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.56,0:10:02.05,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,That's a completely different subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.05,0:10:06.59,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet! I won't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.59,0:10:07.44,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.44,0:10:09.28,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet, yet, yet, yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.28,0:10:10.23,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.27,0:10:16.65,sign_14821_129_December,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,December
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:28.75,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.75,0:10:32.44,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it I still can't use magic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.93,0:10:36.92,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Sister! I'll hang up the laundry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:39.22,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.22,0:10:40.99,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So marry m—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:41.79,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.79,0:10:43.09,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Mar—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.52,0:10:43.48,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.48,0:10:44.34,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Mar—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.34,0:10:45.31,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:48.15,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Marry me, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.20,0:10:51.81,flashback,Rekka,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you start crying, too, Yuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.27,0:10:58.07,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Nash... won't stop crying...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.24,0:11:02.40,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno! Leave this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.12,0:11:06.16,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.16,0:11:09.00,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the Wizard King, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:13.62,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Making a baby or two stop \Ncrying is a piece of cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.62,0:11:18.21,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! There, there! There, there, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.71,0:11:22.72,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.81,0:11:27.20,flashback,Rekka,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:28.68,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.01,0:11:30.25,flashback,Father,0000,0000,0000,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.98,0:11:34.85,flashback,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Hi there. I was wondering if one \Nof you would run an errand for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:37.23,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Me! Me! Me! Me, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.23,0:11:39.08,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.16,0:11:41.69,flashback,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Would someone deliver this to the mayor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.08,0:11:49.52,flashbacktop,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Me, me! Me! Me! Me! Me! Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:47.22,flashback,Father,0000,0000,0000,,It's a very important letter, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.22,0:11:49.52,flashback,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno, could you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.04,0:11:51.50,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:54.67,flashback,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's a very important letter,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.67,0:11:58.04,flashback,Father,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm hesitant to leave it in Asta's \Nhands, so I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.04,0:12:00.96,flashback,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go see the mayor \Nin the next village over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.96,0:12:04.61,flashback,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I have to ask him to spare us some \Nfood to make it through the winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:08.26,flashback,Father,0000,0000,0000,,As it stands now, we just \Ndon't have enough tatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.69,0:12:11.63,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno, I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.51,0:12:17.80,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,No. Father asked me to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.41,0:12:20.02,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.45,0:12:22.07,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be okay by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.52,0:12:23.69,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.69,0:12:25.53,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm heading out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.00,0:12:34.07,flashback,Rekka,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Asta. Chop some wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.07,0:12:37.84,flashback,Rekka,0000,0000,0000,,You can't use magic, so at \Nleast do some manual labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.84,0:12:41.73,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Did you even dig up the \Ntatoes you were supposed to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.73,0:12:43.84,flashback,Rekka,0000,0000,0000,,I dug up the ones for \Ntoday a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.84,0:12:44.92,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.21,0:12:53.11,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it's going \Nto get chilly tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.01,0:13:04.23,flashback,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough! Get out of my shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:07.40,flashback,Man,0000,0000,0000,,The hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.40,0:13:10.60,flashback,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to drink any more, \Nyou gotta bring some cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:12.79,flashback,Owner,0000,0000,0000,,You ain't getting any for free!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:17.46,flashback,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want your stupid \Nbooze anyway, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.33,0:13:22.03,flashback,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.46,0:13:25.01,flashback,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.85,0:13:29.40,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:36.49,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,The snow's getting pretty thick.\NI'll have to be careful not to slip.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.55,0:13:55.37,flashback,Mayor,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you. Please tell \NFather that I received it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.37,0:13:58.67,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I will. P-Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.21,0:14:02.48,flashback,Mayor,0000,0000,0000,,It's late, so be careful getting home!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:05.75,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.81,0:14:27.45,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.31,0:14:34.83,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno's taking an awfully long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:37.08,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.39,0:14:40.53,flashback,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,And Father isn't back yet, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.53,0:14:42.45,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just eat without them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.45,0:14:45.72,flashback,Rekka,0000,0000,0000,,No! That's not fair to Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.72,0:14:46.74,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Boo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.28,0:15:09.76,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,My pendant... That's mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:13.42,flashback,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just gonna exchange it for some cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.42,0:15:14.70,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.51,0:15:22.83,flashback,Man,0000,0000,0000,,You miserable little brat. Where do you\Nget off having something this extravagant?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.17,0:15:26.44,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Give it... back...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.37,0:15:33.92,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.05,0:15:37.29,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,That's mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.05,0:15:41.95,flashback,Man,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:45.73,flashback,Man,0000,0000,0000,,What do you expect to do \Nto me with magic like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.81,0:15:48.40,flashback,Man,0000,0000,0000,,You want to fight me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:50.28,flashback,Man,0000,0000,0000,,and die?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.28,0:16:01.09,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:04.94,flashback,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you, brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:07.04,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's Yuno's!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.04,0:16:09.06,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.36,0:16:10.55,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.39,0:16:15.75,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.51,0:16:20.25,flashback,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me with your filthy hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.25,0:16:23.68,flashback,Man,0000,0000,0000,,You... stupid little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.53,0:16:34.24,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.56,0:16:37.61,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.61,0:16:38.89,flashback,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:42.08,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.08,0:16:43.31,flashback,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.29,0:16:47.71,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:05.91,flashback,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Damn little brat just won't give up.\NWhat the hell's his problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.69,0:17:10.81,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:15.96,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.75,0:17:18.82,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.23,0:17:23.62,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I've got your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.33,0:17:25.47,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:31.37,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta's always done the unthinkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:37.85,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is that grimoire?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.85,0:17:39.30,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,That sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:42.81,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,Just who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.12,0:17:51.10,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,You little wretch with no magical powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.97,0:18:03.05,main,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,He... nullified my magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:11.94,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Even without magical powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:14.50,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to become the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.21,0:18:19.01,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not giving up...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:27.29,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,is my magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.24,0:18:50.62,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I built up my muscles\Nsince I couldn't use any magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.62,0:18:54.53,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they came in handy after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.39,0:18:56.42,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.73,0:19:06.89,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.56,0:19:13.28,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry. It's all \Nmy fault... I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:18.14,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.56,0:19:22.74,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:28.74,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the Wizard King... \Nand protect you and everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.19,0:19:34.03,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna make everyone even happier! \NSo we can have even nicer things!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:38.35,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I'm gonna prove to everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.08,0:19:40.38,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Prove?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.04,0:19:45.47,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That even if you're poor... or an orphan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.71,0:19:49.51,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,you can still become the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:51.54,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,We can?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:52.85,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.33,0:19:55.84,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Can we really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.29,0:20:00.86,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone can... if they work hard enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.76,0:20:03.53,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.53,0:20:06.53,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Me, or even you, Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.41,0:20:16.53,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'll... never cry again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.21,0:20:19.56,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I... no...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.44,0:20:21.55,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:23.14,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.67,0:20:25.80,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become the Wizard King, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.80,0:20:30.62,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get stronger, and protect \Nyou and everyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:34.48,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna make everyone happier! \NSo we can have nicer things!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.56,0:20:43.64,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno! Look, look! I got my own grimoire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.64,0:20:47.73,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's insanely shabby, but I'm gonna take \Ngood care of it for the rest of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.73,0:20:52.09,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,There, there, there, there, there. \NThere, there, there, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:52.09,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.13,0:20:54.72,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,you saved me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:21:00.59,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'll repay you for this someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.08,0:21:03.09,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.93,0:21:07.45,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember our promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.15,0:21:10.60,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So you're gonna become the Wizard King, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.42,0:21:12.43,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.91,0:21:14.33,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.33,0:21:15.43,flashback,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.13,0:21:18.08,flashbackitalics,Both,0000,0000,0000,,...my rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.69,0:21:22.03,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You mean {\i1}you{\i0} remember it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.69,0:21:26.01,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were just making fun of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.67,0:21:30.79,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I have no interest in being \Ntoo friendly with my rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.07,0:21:35.71,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,But you're the one who gave me hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.69,0:21:38.59,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're poor, an orphan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.09,0:21:40.33,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,or even us...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.80,0:21:46.05,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,We can become greater than anyone \Nelse in this world. And to prove that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.60,0:21:50.09,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,To make Sister and everyone else happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.77,0:22:00.10,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see who can become the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.37,0:22:10.98,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can escape from here
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.43,0:22:17.73,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Once again in the small closed off classroom
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.45,0:22:25.96,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The star of the class was shining yet again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.57,0:22:32.42,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,They shine so bright that I close my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.41,0:22:35.85,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I've thought many times
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.17,0:22:39.56,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,That the revolution was within my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.56,0:22:47.16,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it strange? If you want \Nto laugh, go ahead and laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.16,0:22:53.99,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of us who were left \Nbehind wanted to become something
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.30,0:23:01.25,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We repeat the same morning over and over
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.25,0:23:08.13,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who \Ncan choose your tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.44,0:23:12.86,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go beyond our current selves
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.28,0:23:40.00,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I can't use magic,\NI'm going to join the Magic Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.00,0:23:42.41,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So that I can become the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.41,0:23:47.04,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover,{\i0} Page 3: "To the Royal \NCapital of the Clover Kingdom!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.54,0:23:51.39,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 3\N\N{\fs18}To the Royal Capital of the Clover Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.04,0:23:49.96,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not giving up is my magic!
